@startuml
!pragma layout smetana

title Appendix: exhaustive valid ensemble subsets (static ensemble)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam linetype polyline
skinparam rectangle {
  roundCorner 0
  BackgroundColor white
  BorderColor black
  FontColor black
}
skinparam arrowColor black

left to right direction

rectangle "|S| = 2 (n=9)\npair {1,2,3} x {4,5,6}\n\n(1,4) (1,5) (1,6)\n(2,4) (2,5) (2,6)\n(3,4) (3,5) (3,6)" as P2

rectangle "|S| = 3 (n=18)\n2H+1R\n(1,2,4) (1,2,5) (1,2,6) (1,3,4) (1,3,5) (1,3,6) (2,3,4) (2,3,5) (2,3,6)\n1H+2R\n(1,4,5) (1,4,6) (1,5,6) (2,4,5) (2,4,6) (2,5,6) (3,4,5) (3,4,6) (3,5,6)" as P3

rectangle "|S| = 4 (n=15)\n3H+1R\n(1,2,3,4) (1,2,3,5) (1,2,3,6)\n2H+2R\n(1,2,4,5) (1,2,4,6) (1,2,5,6) (1,3,4,5) (1,3,4,6) (1,3,5,6) (2,3,4,5) (2,3,4,6) (2,3,5,6)\n1H+3R\n(1,4,5,6) (2,4,5,6) (3,4,5,6)" as P4

rectangle "|S| = 5 (n=6)\n3H+2R\n(1,2,3,4,5) (1,2,3,4,6) (1,2,3,5,6)\n2H+3R\n(1,2,4,5,6) (1,3,4,5,6) (2,3,4,5,6)" as P5

rectangle "|S| = 6 (n=1)\nfull pool\n\n(1,2,3,4,5,6)" as P6

P2 -[hidden]right- P3
P3 -[hidden]right- P4
P4 -[hidden]right- P5
P5 -[hidden]right- P6

center footer Indices 1-3: historical window; 4-6: recent window. Subset S must intersect both. Total 49 subsets; reported metrics average over all S with the same |S|.

@enduml
